ygData.messageBody:
Thanks Shada :)

Found the song in Erudin but its not nearly as exciting as I thought it was
going to be! Hope you all had a good weekend!

Oh, btw, does anyone know what kind of faction level you need to do the Kael
armor quests? I know that the questgivers USED to be on Tormaxx faction but
apparently they have been swithed to Storm (Kromzek) faction. Does anyon
know whether you need to be "Warmly" or just "Indifferent?"

Thanks!

Halana, 59-60-59-60-59-60 Shaman
Tani, 49th Bard
Solusek Ro
